description.value: You've developed powerful legs capable of leaping great distances. When Leaping horizontally, you move an additional 5 feet. You don't automatically fail your checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.2HJ4yuEFY1Cast4h]{High Jump} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.JUvAvruz7yRQXfz2]{Long Jump} if you don't Stride at least 10 feet first. In addition, when you make a Long Jump, you can jump a distance up to 10 higher than Athletics check result, though still with the normal maximum of your Speed.
